{"about_the_game":"<strong>Planet Zionx, Year 2068, its inhabitants are threatened by an emperor, come to their rescue by offering them food or sleep for example...</strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2357510/extras/title1EN.png?t=1687939887\" /></h2><br>Discover ROMPICHE-8 in full version ! Initially developed for the Gamejam Advance, ROMPICHE-8 is an action-adventure game with an absurd sense of humor in which you play as a robot in charge of bringing peace and rest to the planet Zionx.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2357510/extras/gif.gif?t=1687939887\" /></h2><br>In a gameplay inspired by the FPS of the 90s, you are over-equipped with rest material : <br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Pillows (for sleeping)<br></li><li> Sandwiches (to eat)<br></li><li> And many other weapons ...</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Great for a good night of sleep !</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2357510/extras/title2EN.png?t=1687939887\" /></h2><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2357510/extras/editor.gif?t=1687939887\" /><br>Create your own levels with the MIAMO editor, for increased replayability, then share them with the world on Steam Workshop!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2357510/extras/Frame_30EN.png?t=1687939887\" /></h2><br>Ready for the sandwich race? Discover the different online cooperative and versus modes of ROMPICHE-8!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Modes Planned For Launch </h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Playing the campaign in online coop<br></li><li> Race in a competitive game mode !</li></ul>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2357510/pag